etized, turbulent\ncascade, driven hard by a local energy source and acting jointly with phenomena\nsuch as thermal instability, is the source of these microstructures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Oct 2018 19:44:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-17"}
