ge in the\nbackground magnetic field can lead to another MHD mode number $m$ that ensures\nthe required instability window.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Oct 2018 07:42:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Dec 2018 18:43:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 27 Dec 2018 19:16:32 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 11 Feb 2019 08:32:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-12"}
