y the rigid crosslinkers. This\nleads to a significant increase in cooperativity, on approaching the glass\ntransition, and to a complex behavior that is thoroughly discussed in\ncomparison with those observed in the micro-segregated systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Oct 2018 12:40:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-03"}
