 reach of current detectors, implies almost\ncertainly that typically more than $\\sim 100$ signals of comparable radiated\npower cross the Earth, yet to be discovered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Oct 2018 12:43:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-26"}
