ef review these discoveries and\nlessons learned over the first half a century of Space VLBI. This comparison,\ntogether with the review of technological achievements of the three SLBI\nmissions, creates a fundament for projecting the development of space-based\nradio interferometry into the next decades.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Oct 2018 13:30:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-03"}
