ply adjusting the resolution\nparameter. We therefore argue that they represent two specific levels of a\ncontinuous spectrum 3D communities, rather than seeing them as different\nstructural entities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Oct 2018 14:49:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 May 2019 09:44:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-03"}
